metadata.name: CryptoDials #1
metadata.description: CryptoDials is a Web3 lifestyle brand focused on being the leading watch brand in the crypto space.  CryptoDials leverages blockchain technology to ensure that each physical watch can be authenticated with a chain of title/ownership established on the blockchain. CryptoDials is dedicated to providing a community which brings together enthusiasts from the watch, EDC, photography and other hobbies; creating a space for community members to connect, interact and take their adventures to all new heights.
